# Slide 6
;Mozilla is leading the way in online privacy with browser innovations like Do Not Track and Lightbeam that give users greater control of their personal data.
Mozilla ajk'amöl b'ey pa ruwi' ri ichinanem pa k'amaya'l rik'in taq tz'ukuj pa okik'amaya'l achi'el Do Not Track chuqa' Lightbeam, akuchi' nuya' q'ij chi ke riwinaqi' yekichajij ri taq kitzij.


# Slide 7
;Our global community has helped translate Firefox into over 70 languages, making the browser available to more than 90% of the world's population.
Ri qamoloj aj ruwach'ulew eto'oyon chi rutzalq'omaxik Firefox jotöl chi re ri 70 taq ch'ab'äl, akuchi' niya' pa kiq'a' jotöl chi re ri 90% ruwinaq ri ruwach'ulew.


# Slide 8
;In 2008, 8,002,530 people chose Firefox in a single day to set a Guinness World Record for “Most Downloads of a Software Application in 24 Hours.”
Pa 2008 e 8.002.530 winaqi' xkicha' ri Firefox xa xe pa jun q'ij akuchi' xjikibäx ri Guinness aj ruwach'ulew etal richin “Jotöl ruqasaxik jun ruchokoy kema' pa 24 ramaj.”


# Slide 9
;The Mozilla Festival is our largest annual event, bringing together hundreds of creative minds to realize the full power and potential of the Web.
Ri Mozilla festival, ja ri' ri nïm qamolojri'ïl pa juna', akuchi' nikimöl ki' wok'altäq chi na'owinäq taq winäq richin niq'i' ronojel ri ruchuq'a' chuqa' ruchuq'ab'il Ajk'amaya'l.


# Slide 10
;Mozilla Webmaker works to create a more Web-literate planet, providing tools and projects to help people take greater control of their online lives.
Ri rurayb'al Mozilla Webmaker ja ri nisamäj pa ruwi' jun utziläj kajulew, akuchi' e k'ïy ketaman pa ruwi' ri kematz'ib', chuqa' akuchi' niya' taq samajib'äl chuqa' taq nimasamaj, ri yekito' ri winaqi' chi tik'oje' pa kiq'a' ri kik'aslema kik'in kematz'ib'.


# Slide 11
