Firefox richin Android nuk'äm pe ri retamab'al Firefox richin ajkematz'ib' pa taq oyonib'äl chuqa' pa taq tz'alamkem. Wachel pa Google Play, qasan chik jotöl chi re ri 80 t'ijtäq mul.


